gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

I have attained peace, O Umaya Bai; God is present there;
I am seated in spiritual sight, none can measure my joy.

Here is the translation:

You got bread as a gift, obtained village as a gift from Brahmin; 
Those sitting there are Umaya Bai's sisters, where you put your wealth, that's over there.

Here is the translation:

That is the gift of birth anniversary, that is the blessing; 
He who is fed with fragrance, is not held on his head by others.

Here is the translation:

Your blessing done, Oh Lord, now go to your home; 
Come only Ummayad in my body, bring blessing there.

What to ask you, Uma, that you should know; 
You have known the suspicion kept by my husband. 
Uma says my time has come, she asks when it will be, this year will pass.
